@startuml TxStateMachine
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam state {
  FontSize 12
  FontName Consolas
  BackgroundColor #EEF2FF
  BorderColor #445566
}

title ISOTP Transmitter FSM (HFSM2)
\n\n
state Idle : Waiting for send request
state SendSingleFrame : Sending SF frame (data <= 7 bytes)
state SendFirstFrame : Sending FF frame (data > 7 bytes)
state WaitFlowControl : Waiting for FC after FF or after block
state SendConsecutiveFrame : Sending CF frame(s)
state TxCompleted : Send completed
state TxError : Error state\n\n
[*] --> Idle : Initial entry\n\n
Idle --> SendSingleFrame : SendRequest && size <= 7
Idle --> SendFirstFrame : SendRequest && size > 7\n\n
SendSingleFrame --> TxCompleted : Frame sent

SendFirstFrame --> WaitFlowControl : FF sent\n\n
WaitFlowControl --> SendConsecutiveFrame : RxFrame(FC, CTS)
WaitFlowControl --> WaitFlowControl : RxFrame(FC, WAIT) - restart timer
WaitFlowControl --> TxError : RxFrame(FC, OVERFLOW)
WaitFlowControl --> TxError : Timeout(N_Bs)\n\n
SendConsecutiveFrame --> SendConsecutiveFrame : TxConfirmation OK && more data && (no block limit)
SendConsecutiveFrame --> WaitFlowControl : TxConfirmation OK && blockSize > 0 && blockCounter >= blockSize
SendConsecutiveFrame --> TxCompleted : TxConfirmation OK && all data sent
SendConsecutiveFrame --> TxError : TxConfirmation FAIL
SendConsecutiveFrame --> TxError : Timeout(N_Cs)\n\n
SendConsecutiveFrame --> WaitFlowControl : ReadyToSend after STmin (auto transition)\n\n
TxCompleted --> Idle : auto\n\n
Idle --> Idle : Reset
WaitFlowControl --> Idle : Reset
SendConsecutiveFrame --> Idle : Reset
TxError --> Idle : Reset\n\n
TxError --> TxError : any other event\n\n
@enduml